name: SEOClock.co.uk
tag_list: seo, seo-sheffield, search-engine-optimization, website-marketing, internet-marketing, website-design, sheffield
overview:
This firm has a cumulative experience of over 20 years in SEO (search engine optimization). They are based in the City of Sheffield, in the UK. SEO’Clock specialise in the optimization of small to medium size businesses in the Yorkshire and Derbyshire areas.

Started by Neil Palmer, the company was founded to offer a professional service to local companies, at a time when there was a lack of options in this relatively new industry. Since then SEO’Clock have moved into social media, website design and now offer a complete marketing service.

The key staff for SEO’Clock cover all aspects of managing SEO campaigns, including CSS web design, html coding, Javascript, blogging and content writing.
